          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm;">Get AI suggestions for visual content based on your brand.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-hover bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600">
